{"tid":2282991,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"又到年尾清假嘅時候","createTime":"2020-11-12T08:50:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T14:40:24.000Z","uid":6399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3611633068832c5252fc80ad8e6c97b1ef721932","tid":2282991,"uid":6399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T08:50:58.000Z","msg":"話說做咗呢間公司準備一年<br />\nAL得勞工法例嘅七日<br />\n<br />\n我想請假嗰時我 上司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同 我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你知唔知你唔放AL係可以出返錢畀你？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我知呀但我覺得放假開心啲喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人公司都係咁<br />\n唔畀儲假 年尾有剩假就畀返錢你？<br />\n將你份糧除三十日再計返你剩幾多日假<br />\n<br />\n我諗人工高嘅先會想袋返錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"facc6e09ca848ff88f8ffe7f594bd3d9ace1b974","tid":2282991,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T08:52:24.000Z","msg":"低人工先想袋"},{"pid":"693019d82e0cc0d2c44f4a0358c0547016ed12ea","tid":2282991,"uid":6399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"facc6e09ca848ff88f8ffe7f594bd3d9ace1b974","tid":2282991,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T08:52:24.000Z","msg":"低人工先想袋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T08:55:47.000Z","msg":"低人工份糧除三十日都係得好少錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa72f6d628d99f3dac720751499e5982fffa7e3","tid":2282991,"uid":10340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T08:56:02.000Z","msg":"你咪算好囉, 可以俾翻錢你, 我公司政策係:上年有淨嘅年假, 今年唔清嘅話就自動waive左,無錢補翻."},{"pid":"da3134291e52ed815db2bc2999a088e6dcdcfe8c","tid":2282991,"uid":116960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fa72f6d628d99f3dac720751499e5982fffa7e3","tid":2282991,"uid":10340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0